{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_11_02",
  "title": "天動瑠依 2話 エッチなイメージなんですね",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――脚本のサンプルが届いてすぐ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― Shortly after the script sample arrived",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日はレッスンルームで、瑠依がサキュバス役の）\n（練習をしているんだったな……様子を見てみるか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Today‚ Rui is in the lesson room practicing）\n（for her Succubus role… Let's see how she's doing.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "「わ、私のも、ものに……\nし、してあげてもいい、わ、よ」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"M-Make… make me…\"\n\"y-yours… if you w-want.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……全然ダメだわ。『誘惑するように』って……\n一体どうすればいいのよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's no good at all. \"As if seducing\"…\nHow on earth am I supposed to do that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3233.333333400001,
          "startTime": 26.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "こっちのセリフは……「そ、そんなことも\n出来ないなんて、私が、いないとダメなの、ね……？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This line is… \"I-If you can't even\ndo that‚ you're hopeless without me‚ aren't y-you…?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.5625870377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "「さぁ、ひ、ひざまじゅっ……ひざまずいてっ！\nわ、私のく、く、靴……靴を舐め、なさい……」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Now‚ k-kneel… Kneel down!\"\n\"L-Lick… lick my s-shoes…\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（……どうしたんだ？　やけにぎこちないな）\n（演技は苦手じゃなかったはずだけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…What's going on? She's incredibly stiff.）\n（She shouldn't be bad at acting‚ but…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！　{user}さん！？\nい、いつからそこに……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah! {user}!?\nS-Since when were you there…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "うっ、そんな目で見ないで下さい\n……自分でも全然ダメだって分かっています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ please don't look at me like that.\n…I'm well aware that I'm doing a terrible job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "役作りに難航しているようだな……\n瑠依はまだサキュバスに抵抗があるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems you're having trouble with the character development…\nDo you still feel some resistance to the Succubus role‚ Rui?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、もう気持ちは固まっています。むしろ今は\nしっかり役作りに取り組みたいんです、けど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ my mind is made up. Rather‚ right now\nI want to focus properly on building the character‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "真面目にやろうとすればするほど、恥ずかしくなって\n……自分でも迷走している自覚は、あります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The more serious I try to be‚ the more embarrassed I get.\n…I'm aware that I'm just wandering aimlessly here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……。でも、やる気はこの間より\nさらに増しているみたいだな。何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see…. But your motivation seems to have\nincreased even more since the other day. Did something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "実は、配役が決まってから\n同じサキュバス役の千紗と、話をしたんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ after the roles were decided‚\nI talked with Chisa‚ who's also playing a Succubus.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "「ちょっと恥ずかしいけど、応援してきてくれた\n人達へのお返しになるなら頑張る」と言っていて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She said‚ \"It's a bit embarrassing‚ but I'll work hard\nif it's a way to give back to those who support me.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "その時、痛感したんです。私は千紗ほど覚悟が決まって\nいなかった。ファンへの気持ちも中途半端だったって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At that moment‚ I realized it. I wasn't as prepared\nas Chisa‚ and my feelings for the fans were half-hearted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "サキュバスで、その……エ、エッチなのは\nやっぱりまだ、恥ずかしいですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Playing a Succubus‚ and being… l-lewd…\nit's still embarrassing‚ after all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.3666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくファンと一緒に作るゲームなんですから\n私も、少しでもファンにお返しがしたいと思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But since it's a game made together with the fans‚\nI also wanted to give back to them as much as possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.6721720286,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4242.274230000021,
          "startTime": 134.9144462586
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "でも……この『上から目線で小馬鹿にするように』とか\n『惑わすように』っていう演技が分からなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… I don't understand the acting for \"Looking down on them\"\nor \"Seducing them\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.5333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "強引に迫るシーンも多いですし……\n生意気で偉そうで、傲慢なだけに思えてしまって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are many scenes where I'm aggressively approaching…\nIt just feels saucy‚ arrogant‚ and haughty to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.9075392527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私が演じるキャラクターの見た目なんですけど\n肌の露出が多くて、自分だと思うと恥ずかしくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ concerning the appearance of the character I'm playing‚\nthere's a lot of skin showing. Thinking of it as myself is embarrassing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.627089873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。まだキャラを掴めていないってことか\n俺は瑠依にピッタリだと思ったんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. So you haven't grasped the character yet.\nI thought it was perfect for you‚ Rui…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.8212859333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "どこがピッタリなんですか！？　……え？\nまさか私、生意気で偉そうで傲慢なんですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How is it perfect for me!? …Eh?\nDo you mean I'm saucy‚ arrogant‚ and haughty…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.0666753133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それはどちらかというとkanaさんとか……ゴホン\nいや、瑠依がそういう性格だって話じゃないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's more like kana-san… Ahem\nNo‚ I didn't mean you have that kind of personality.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.7333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんに聞かれたら大変なことになりそうですが\n……では、どういう意味ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kana-san would be furious if she heard that‚ but…\n…Then‚ what do you mean by that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.7000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、そうだな……うまく言えないけど、まずは\n演じるキャラクターへの理解を深めてみたらどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ right…. I can't explain it well‚ but first‚\nwhy don't you try deepening your understanding of the character?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.4094403386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "今の瑠依は、「サキュバスというのはこういうものだ」\nっていうイメージに、囚われ過ぎているように見える",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ you seem too trapped in the image\nthat \"A Succubus is like this.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.1666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_11_02-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "……言われてみれば私、イメージだけで知った気に\nなっていて、深くは知らないかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Now that you mention it‚ I might have felt like I knew\neverything just from the image‚ without knowing deeply.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.6723912321,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7432.791274199985,
          "startTime": 219.1051825063
        }
      ]
    },
